    - target: {fileID: 7072880099072085984, guid: ce852e3a197f03c418363d6dceb2438b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: "<b>Controls:</b>\nWASD \u2013 Move forward/backward/left/right\r\nShift
        \u2013 Sprint (speed boost)\r\nSpace \u2013 Move up\r\nCtrl \u2013 Move down\r\nZ
        \u2013 Zoom in/out\r\nMouse \u2013 Look around\r\nTab \u2013 Show cursor
        / pause camera rotation (press and hold)\nNote: When Tab is held, the cursor
        becomes visible and you can interact with UI elements. Release Tab to resume
        camera control."
